Project Name: Freelancer Jobseeker Website

Introduction
This project is a freelancer/jobseeker website that provides a platform for individuals to showcase their skills and find job opportunities. It allows freelancers/jobseekers to create profiles, upload portfolios, and connect with potential clients/employers. The website is built using HTML, CSS, JavaScript, the Bootstrap framework, and jQuery libraries.

Deployed Site
You can access the deployed site marys24.tech.

